---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/ui/CTASection.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/ui/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import TestimonialsSection from '../../components/sections/TestimonialsSection.astro';

const city = "Hackensack";
const title = "CPA in Hackensack NJ | Tax & Accounting Services | ProAxis";
const description = "ProAxis provides expert CPA services in Hackensack NJ — tax preparation, tax planning, bookkeeping, and business accounting for Hackensack businesses and residents. 100% virtual.";
const canonical = "/service-areas/hackensack/";
const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: "Service Areas", url: "/service-areas/" },
  { name: city }
];
const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": ["LocalBusiness", "AccountingService"],
  "name": "ProAxis Tax & Accounting Services",
  "telephone": "+12018002330",
  "email": "info@proaxiscpa.com",
  "url": "https://www.proaxiscpa.com",
  "address": {
    "@type": "PostalAddress",
    "addressLocality": "Hasbrouck Heights",
    "addressRegion": "NJ",
    "postalCode": "07604",
    "addressCountry": "US"
  },
  "areaServed": { "@type": "City", "name": "Hackensack, NJ" }
};
---

<BaseLayout {title} {description} {canonical} {schema} {breadcrumbs}>
  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbs} />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1C1C1E 0%, #2E75B6 100%);" class="py-14 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold mb-4" style="background-color: rgba(197,165,90,0.2); color: #C5A55A;">
        Serving {city}, NJ &bull; 100% Virtual
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold font-heading text-white mb-4">CPA &amp; Accounting Services in {city}, NJ</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8">ProAxis delivers expert tax preparation, tax planning, bookkeeping, and business advisory to {city} businesses and residents — all virtually, all on your schedule.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-white" style="background-color: #22C55E;">Schedule Free Consultation</a>
        <a href="tel:+12018002330" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-white border-2 border-white/40">Call (201) 800-2330</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 lg:py-16">

    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Hackensack's Business Landscape</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Hackensack is Bergen County's county seat and largest city — a distinction that gives it a unique economic character unlike any other community in the county. The Bergen County courthouse complex on Main Street draws a steady ecosystem of attorneys, bail bondsmen, process servers, court reporters, private investigators, and legal support businesses. If you run a professional services firm adjacent to the Bergen County court system, your revenue patterns, deductible expenses, and entity structure deserve careful attention from a CPA who understands that specific economic context.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The main commercial spine of Hackensack runs along Main Street and State Street through downtown, where you'll find a mix of established retail, restaurants, professional offices, and government-related services. In recent years, Hackensack's downtown has benefited from a sustained revitalization effort, with new residential development, updated streetscaping, and an influx of food and beverage businesses that cater to the working population during weekday lunch hours and the growing residential population on evenings and weekends. New businesses opening downtown often need help structuring their entities properly, setting up accounting systems, and understanding Hackensack's local business licensing requirements alongside their NJ and federal obligations.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Hackensack University Medical Center is one of Bergen County's largest employers and a major force in the local economy. The HUMC campus and the broader Hackensack Meridian Health network attract and support an enormous ecosystem of medical professionals — physicians running independent practices, specialist groups, medical billing companies, healthcare technology consultants, and allied health businesses. Medical professional practice accounting is a specialized area: overhead cost tracking, professional liability insurance deductions, retirement plan selection (defined benefit plans can be highly advantageous for high-earning physicians), and eventual practice sale or valuation planning all require expertise that goes well beyond standard business tax preparation.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The Route 4 and Route 17 corridors near Hackensack are dense with commercial real estate — office parks, retail strips, industrial flex space, and automotive businesses. Commercial property owners in this area face NJ-specific depreciation and cost recovery considerations, as well as potential 1031 exchange opportunities when properties change hands. If you own commercial real estate in or around Hackensack, proactive tax planning around cost basis, depreciation recapture, and capital gains timing is essential.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">The Korean-American business community along Anderson Street and in the surrounding area represents one of Hackensack's most entrepreneurially vibrant corridors. First-generation business owners running restaurants, beauty supply businesses, import/export companies, and specialty retail face a combination of bookkeeping challenges (high transaction volume, inventory management, cash-intensive businesses) and opportunities (Section 179 equipment deductions, self-employed retirement plan contributions, home office deductions for hybrid operations) that reward working with a CPA who takes the time to understand their specific business model.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Tax &amp; Accounting Needs in Hackensack</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Hackensack's blend of government-adjacent professional services, major healthcare employers, commercial real estate activity, and diverse small business ownership creates tax situations that span the full complexity spectrum. Here are the areas where Hackensack clients most often benefit from proactive CPA engagement:</p>
    <ul class="list-none space-y-3 mb-6">
      {[
        { heading: "S-Corp and LLC tax elections", text: "Many Hackensack professionals and business owners are operating as sole proprietors or single-member LLCs and missing the self-employment tax savings available through a properly structured S-Corp election." },
        { heading: "Healthcare industry deductions", text: "Medical and healthcare professionals have access to significant deductions — continuing education, professional licenses, malpractice insurance, medical equipment, and employer retirement plans — that are frequently underutilized." },
        { heading: "NJ sales and use tax compliance", text: "Retail businesses and service companies with taxable NJ transactions need clean quarterly sales tax filing. Errors compound quickly and draw scrutiny from the NJ Division of Taxation." },
        { heading: "County government contractors", text: "Businesses that contract with Bergen County or its agencies often have unique invoicing, retainage, and revenue recognition patterns that affect when income is recognized and taxed." },
        { heading: "Multistate income allocation", text: "Businesses serving clients in both NJ and NY — common in Hackensack given the county's proximity to New York City — need to correctly apportion income across state lines to avoid double taxation." },
      ].map((item) => (
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg" style="background-color: #F7F8FA;">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0" style="background-color: #C5A55A;"></div>
          <div><span class="font-semibold" style="color: #1C1C1E;">{item.heading}:</span> <span class="text-gray-700">{item.text}</span></div>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>

    <!-- ProAxis Services -->
    <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 mb-10" style="background-color: #F7F8FA;">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">ProAxis Serves Hackensack Businesses &amp; Residents</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">ProAxis Tax &amp; Accounting Services brings Bergen County expertise to Hackensack businesses and individuals through our fully virtual delivery model. Whether you're a solo attorney working near the courthouse, a physician with privileges at HUMC, a Korean restaurant owner on Anderson Street, or a Hackensack resident with a complex federal and NJ tax return, we're equipped to serve you.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-5">
        {[
          { name: "Tax Preparation", link: "/tax-services/tax-preparation/" },
          { name: "Tax Planning", link: "/tax-services/tax-planning/" },
          { name: "Bookkeeping", link: "/business-services/bookkeeping/" },
          { name: "Business Advisory", link: "/business-services/" },
          { name: "NJ SALT Consulting", link: "/tax-services/nj-salt-consulting/" },
          { name: "Fractional CFO", link: "/business-services/fractional-cfo/" },
        ].map((svc) => (
          <a href={svc.link} class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-white border border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-300 font-medium transition-all" style="color: #2E75B6;">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
            {svc.name}
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Why Choose a Virtual CPA in Hackensack</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Hackensack has no shortage of accounting firms — it's Bergen County's largest city with a dense professional services sector. But volume doesn't always translate to value. Many traditional CPA firms in Hackensack operate on a reactive, tax-season-only model: they prepare your return in the spring, you don't hear from them until the following January, and whatever tax-saving opportunities arose during the year were missed because no one was watching.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">ProAxis operates differently. Our virtual model allows us to maintain an ongoing advisory relationship with clients throughout the year — quarterly check-ins, proactive planning conversations when major financial events arise, and rapid response when you have a tax question that needs an answer before you sign a contract or make a business decision.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">For Hackensack business owners who are already spending their days navigating one of Bergen County's busiest commercial environments, the ability to handle your accounting relationship entirely online — without fighting Hackensack traffic, paying for downtown parking, or blocking out a Tuesday morning — is a meaningful quality-of-life improvement.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-5" style="color: #1C1C1E;">Nearby Areas We Also Serve</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">In addition to Hackensack, ProAxis provides CPA services throughout Bergen County and surrounding areas. If your business or residence is near Hackensack, we're ready to help:</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-8">
      {[
        { name: "Teaneck", slug: "teaneck" },
        { name: "Englewood", slug: "englewood" },
        { name: "Paramus", slug: "paramus" },
        { name: "Bergen County (all)", slug: "bergen-county" },
      ].map((area) => (
        <a href={`/service-areas/${area.slug}/`} class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border hover:shadow-sm transition-all" style="border-color: #2E75B6; color: #2E75B6; background-color: rgba(46,117,182,0.05);">{area.name}</a>
      ))}
    </div>
    <p class="text-gray-700">Ready to get started? <a href="/contact/" class="font-medium underline" style="color: #2E75B6;">Schedule a free consultation</a> with ProAxis today, or explore our <a href="/tax-services/" class="font-medium underline" style="color: #2E75B6;">full range of tax services</a>.</p>
  </article>

  <TestimonialsSection />
  <CTASection heading={"CPA Services in " + city + ", NJ — Schedule Your Free Consultation"} />
</BaseLayout>
